{"bio":null,"bio_l":"恐怖利刃是恶魔中的掠夺者——这个无法无天的魔头就连恶魔都惧怕三分。他曾因对恶魔领主动了贼念，无视了所有规范他行为的基本法则，触犯了七度地狱的所有法规。他被好好上了一课：原来还有比地狱更可怕的地方。接下来是短暂又残酷的审问，最终他被打入了荒邪之狱，这是一个隐藏的位面，恶魔们将它们的同类囚禁在这里。荒邪之狱并不是普通的监狱，这是现实的暗黑镜像，恶魔经过判决都到这里来直视他们自身灵魂中的扭曲倒影。然而恐怖利刃不但没有受苦，反而将自身最邪恶的倒影转化成了操控自如的力量，并将他的恐怖全数释放。","stats":"<img src=\"Int\" alt=\"Intelligence\" />Intelligence:19 + 1.75<br /><img src=\"Agi\" alt=\"Agility\" />Agility:22 + 3.20<br /><img src=\"Str\" alt=\"Strength\" />Strength:15 + 1.40<br /><img src=\"Attack\" alt=\"Damage\" />Damage:26 - 32<br /><img src=\"Speed\" alt=\"Movespeed\" />Movespeed:315<br /><img src=\"Defense\" alt=\"Armor\" />Armor:7.08","stats1":[["Int","Intelligence","19 + 1.75"],["Agi","Agility","22 + 3.20"],["Str","Strength","15 + 1.40"],["Attack","Damage","26 - 32"],["Speed","Movespeed","315"],["Defense","Armor","7.08"]],"detailstats":"<div class=\"redboxContent\"><div class=\"redboxTop\"></div><div id=\"statsInner\"><div id=\"statsLeft\"><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol\">25</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">15</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">1</div>等级</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,453</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">807</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">435</div>生命值</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,053</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">566</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">247</div>魔法值</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">145-151</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">93-99</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">48-54</div>攻击力</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">21</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">13</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">7</div>护甲</div></div><div id=\"statsRight\"><div class=\"statRow\"></div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">1800 / 800</div>视野范围</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">128</div>攻击范围</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">900</div>弹道速度</div></div><br clear=\"both\" /></div><div class=\"redboxBottom\"></div></div>","detailst